[72.070322, "o", "[35m.brainyard/agents/research-agent/add-format-text-json-option-cli/dossier.md\\nPurpose: Research what it\u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mwould take to add a --format {text,json} option to this CLI (RECOMMEND only — no code\u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mwrites).\\nAcceptance focus: a1 (map all greeting format/render sites + CLI arg parsing with path+line\u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mcitations).\\nHint: Focus on greeting output functions, render/print sites, and the CLI arg-parsing layer.\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mCite paths and line ranges so the plan specialist can reference exact touch points.\"}))\u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(println explore-result)\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m└─\u001b[0m\u001b[35;3H"]
