[123.596136, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m┌─\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(def explore-result\u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  (explore-agent\u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    {:question \"Map how greetings are CURRENTLY formatted and rendered across this CLI project. Identify,\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mwith file path + line citations: (1) every function/site that produces or formats a greeting string, (2)\u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mevery site that renders/prints greeting output to the user, (3) the existing CLI argument parsing setup\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(where flags/options are defined and dispatched), and (4) any existing notion of output format. Goal is\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mto understand all touch points a new --format {text,json} option would need to thread through. Read-only\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35msurvey — do not propose changes.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m     :agent-context \"Research dossier:\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m.brainyard/agents/res"]
