[524.029299, "o", "2m│\u001b[0m      silently dropping the parsed flag. Pass \u001b[36mfmt=args.format\u001b[0m.                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   3. \u001b[1;97mAdd the json branch\u001b[0m — extend \u001b[36mrender()\u001b[0m at \u001b[36msrc/formatters.py:8-12\u001b[0m (currently text-only) with a \u001b[36mjson\u001b[0m       \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m      branch that serializes the greeting.                                                                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   4. \u001b[1;97mProducer unchanged\u001b[0m — \u001b[36mformat_greeting()\u001b[0m at \u001b[36msrc/util.py:1-3\u001b[0m needs no change.                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   5. \u001b[1;97mManual verification only\u001b[0m — no automated test suite exists in the repo.                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mCaveats\u001b[0m                                   "]
[524.029373, "o", "                                                                   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[1;97mOrdering matters\u001b[0m — adding the renderer branch before the wiring fix (step 2) leaves the flag dead.       \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[1;97mNo test suite\u001b[0m — manual CLI runs are the only safety net.                                                 \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[1;97mOpen question\u001b[0m — confirm the exact JSON shape (single key vs. structured fields) before implementation.   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mArtifacts\u001b[0m                                                                                                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • Plan: \u001b[36m.brainyard/agents/plan-agent/plans/ivory-elk-5720.md\u001b[0m                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b"]
